{"tid":1595933,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"陳雲：據傳，養龜陳流亡海外。成為陳雲海外暗黑弟子，前途好過在水泉澳。","createTime":"2019-09-26T09:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T10:33:02.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"53cca9ce2895639469d1f7aa3f6c07d975d5e8d3","tid":1595933,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:36:24.000Z","msg":"陳雲：據傳，養龜陳流亡海外。成為陳雲海外暗黑弟子，前途好過在水泉澳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【絕密消息 陳浩天計劃棄保潛逃】<br />\n在反修例運動如火如荼，被捕人士愈來愈多，暴力程度不斷升級之際，圈中人收到從未曝光的消息，陳浩天計劃棄保潛逃！<br />\n據了解，台獨組織「獨立公投人權運動」邀請陳浩天參加在台北市西華飯店舉行的「9.29」活動，形式是「演講餐會」，主辦方成員包括江蓋世、陳嘉霖、潘厚勳、陳正德、吳栢宏，更會有吳澧培、洪清森、劉宜俊等一眾金主慷慨解囊。<br />\n重要的是，陳浩天正加緊聯繫台灣、德國、日本政府官員及其他獨派人士，希望爭取「政治難民」身份，借道台灣出國，逃避香港的法律責任，棄保潛逃。<br />\n據陳浩天身邊人說，佢認為台灣「唔夠安全」，不宜久留，所以真正目標係德國或者日本。<br />\n當示威者不斷犧牲的時候，原來陳浩天已在計劃「走佬」，正所謂「笨人出手，精人出走」，大家點睇？"},{"pid":"04002af4c1508d31fbab527602f231261115160d","tid":1595933,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae4d54643626c657ee503196f0a95aa4461dbcc","tid":1595933,"uid":201464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/152112_1520d0fcbdd664fd69334cedb9a7a064.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F152112_1520d0fcbdd664fd69334cedb9a7a064.jpg&h=d30124ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aOP2WSX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaOP2WSX.jpg&h=04383e39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋麻煩以後要睇陳雲偉論請去高登會員香江19度睇，直程係陳雲代言人<br />\n<a href=\"https://newweb.hkgolden.com/user/403064/posthistory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewweb.hkgolden.com%2Fuser%2F403064%2Fposthistory&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=e61e4503\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newweb.hkgolden.com/user/403064/posthistory</a>"},{"pid":"3abdc1de9de7cc10ffcbb4392e267d95c27d1d33","tid":1595933,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T10:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b5463838a776df040bc0a5e956338026796b68","tid":1595933,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T10:33:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">陳雲熱狗抹黑連登，<br />\n請返回高登<br />\n不推文回覆</span>"}]}